      "message": "I really don\u0027t think a test function would be more readable.\n\nAs an example, the table entry below\n\n  {\n    name: \"above both MaxDifferentPixels and PixelDeltaThreshold, returns false\",\n    imageBytes: imageToPngBytes(t, text.MustToNRGBA(`! SKTEXTSIMPLE\n    2 2\n    0x00000506 0x00000001\n    0x00000001 0x00000000`)),\n    expected: false,\n  },\n\nwould become\n\n  test(\n    \"above both MaxDifferentPixels and PixelDeltaThreshold, returns false\",\n    imageToPngBytes(t, text.MustToNRGBA(`! SKTEXTSIMPLE\n    2 2\n    0x00000506 0x00000001\n    0x00000001 0x00000000`)),\n    false)\n\nwhich IMO is less readable due to the lack of the named fields.\n\nWDYT?",
